public enum VehicleStopMode extends Enum<VehicleStopMode>

  • Enum Constant Details

    • NOT_STOPPED

      public static final VehicleStopMode NOT_STOPPED
      Vehicle is not/will not be stopped.

    • STOP

      public static final VehicleStopMode STOP
      Stops the vehicle on the specified lane index. Other vehicles, which approach behind the stopped vehicle, might be disrupted.

    • PARK_ON_ROADSIDE

      public static final VehicleStopMode PARK_ON_ROADSIDE
      Parks the vehicle at the road side. Other vehicles won't be disrupted by the parking vehicle.

    • BUS_STOP

      public static final VehicleStopMode BUS_STOP
      Stops the vehicle at a bus or train stop.

    • PARK_IN_PARKING_AREA

      public static final VehicleStopMode PARK_IN_PARKING_AREA
      Parks the vehicle at a parking area. The vehicle has to be close to the parking area.
